  <h2>Why Sellers Benefit</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Fewer surprises.</strong> Knowing the condition avoids a last-minute discovery during the buyer's inspection.</li>
    <li><strong>Documentation.</strong> Records and a recent inspection reassure buyers.</li>
    <li><strong>Time to act.</strong> Any issues can be addressed on your schedule, not under deadline pressure.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Getting Ready to List</h2>
